query: SELECT pa.id as aliasId, pa.alias, pa.playerId, p.id, p.name, p.team, p.overall, p.isRookie, p.draftYear FROM player_aliases pa JOIN players p ON pa.playerId = p.id WHERE pa.alias = 'Richard' ORDER BY p.name
